BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313269320@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T000654Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T160000
SUMMARY:English Country Dance Marin
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nEnglish country dancing is done in long lines (like contra)\, circles\, or in geometric sets (squares\, triangles). Like our contra dances\, there is live music and a caller. You can come by yourself or with friends\, since we change partners after each dance. If you’ve ever done contra or square dancing\, much of our dance vocabulary will be familiar to you since both of those styles evolved from English country dancing.\n\nAdmission is $15 for members of NBCDS and its affiliates.
