BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313269346@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T000654Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T190000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260314T220000
SUMMARY:San Rafael Contra Dance
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nContra Dance is fun\, quick to learn\, and great exercise. Every dance night has a live band\, caller\, and a quick start class for first timers.\nIn contra dance\, you will dance with your partner but also with other couples as you progress down the line. The figures for each dance are done in a repeated sequence after a brief walk through by the caller. Each dance may last 10 – 12 minutes and then we encourage you to switch partners as the night goes on.\nWhat to wear: Comfortable shoes that will enable you to pivot and slide on the wood floor.\nWhen to arrive: If this is your first time\, come 30 minutes early to check in\, join the quick start class\, and get you ready for the first dance.\nHow hard to learn? Most newcomers will find that they can get dancing right away as the figures are quite simple.\nCome as a group\, couple\, or single! Our dance is inclusive to all ages and genders.\nCost: *Free to first-time dancers*. $13 members\, $15 non-members\, $8 student or limited income.
URL;VALUE=URI:https://www.meetup.com/north-bay-contra-dance/events/313269346/
STATUS:CONFIRMED
CREATED:20260208T204233Z
LAST-MODIFIED:20260208T204233Z
CLASS:PUBLIC
