END:VEVENT
BEGIN:VEVENT
UID:event_313269351@meetup.com
SEQUENCE:1
DTSTAMP:20260309T000654Z
DTSTART;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260315T140000
DTEND;TZID=America/Los_Angeles:20260315T163000
SUMMARY:English Country Dance Sebastopol
DESCRIPTION:North Bay Contra Dance\nEnglish country dancing is done in long lines (like contra)\, circles\, or in geometric sets (squares\, triangles). Like our contra dances\, there is live music and a caller. You can come by yourself or with friends\, since we change partners after each dance. If you’ve ever done contra or square dancing\, much of our dance vocabulary will be familiar to you since both of those styles evolved from English country dancing.\n\nThe dance is held the 1st and 3rd Sundays of each month\, 2-4:30 pm\, to live music\, all levels of experience welcome\; and occasional 5th Sundays for Advanced dancers. Admission is $15 for members of NBCDS and its affiliates\, $8 for young adults ages 19-30\, and $3 for youth ages 6 – 18.
